{"id": "1418510528275546203", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束**\n花园是一道谜题，玫瑰是她的答案。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: Horla EP: A Bouquet for \"Spring\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: Horla EP: A Bouquet for \"Spring\"**\nThe Garden is a puzzle, and Rose its last piece.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:14:24.592000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}, {"emoji": "cough", "emoji_id": "1356082510928543834", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Sendflowers", "emoji_id": "1400771545370067118", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1418510529785237647", "filename": "OST-250827-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2731763, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418510529785237647/OST-250827-.jpg?ex=69ccd3e0&is=69cb8260&hm=d500976bb10e2c2f7bb2bc5f5351123a3548d25d9c6c6d629c7a29a47baade33&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418511049791111269", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.花房晨曦-Morning in the Flower House-**\n\n阳光透过花房的玻璃照在奥尔拉的脸上。她穿过阳光，来到睡意朦胧的奥尔拉身前。\n每次唤醒她的时候，她都将玫瑰藏于身后。\n\nThe sunlight streams through the conservatory glass, falling upon Horla's face. She steps through the light to find a sleepy Horla. \nEvery time Colette wakes her up, she makes sure to hide a rose behind her back.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:16:28.931000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418511049178615838", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1725126, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511049178615838/1.jpg?ex=69ccd45c&is=69cb82dc&hm=55b6dff7faaabd1addc03dc34eb4cac6d84d90addb4841f2985696d4e5dc7730&"}, {"id": "1418511049534996531", "filename": "1.-Morning_in_the_Flower_House-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1356738, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511049534996531/1.-Morning_in_the_Flower_House-.mp3?ex=69ccd45c&is=69cb82dc&hm=6ac444f70d0d297034255ef28575f2344a7767cdf4f341ed28d78df18bda84e2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418511160122015828", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.诗页的余烬-Embers of a Poem-**\n\n她将花园的故事写入诗页。\n她将花园的故事投入火堆。\n\nShe writes the garden's stories onto a page.\nShe casts the garden's stories into the fire.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:16:55.236000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418511159333748756", "filename": "2.-Embers_of_a_Poem-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1775533, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511159333748756/2.-Embers_of_a_Poem-.mp3?ex=69ccd477&is=69cb82f7&hm=dba9029a0dcf3eb93de064a85f1fa3336bc9528631d89dae82f4e46116118a73&"}, {"id": "1418511159790800896", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1712475, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511159790800896/2.jpg?ex=69ccd477&is=69cb82f7&hm=477c34447887fc693a2a56dc0e78255987954d402c2931b1a74c4de30a530d8b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418511273422753882", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03.两个人的春日-A Spring for Two-    **\n\n握住我的手吧。\n当手指相碰的时候，我将赠你一个春天。\n\nHold my hand.\nAnd when our fingers touch, I shall gift you a Spring.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:17:22.249000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418511272781021246", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1711948, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511272781021246/3.jpg?ex=69ccd492&is=69cb8312&hm=a08bbcf0e9d9308d43d1da7029e40dd4d921e82e9ecbb53eb82d072b247d6223&"}, {"id": "1418511273091530763", "filename": "3.-A_Spring_for_Two-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1477946, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511273091530763/3.-A_Spring_for_Two-.mp3?ex=69ccd492&is=69cb8312&hm=8d6128f8534a07cea2cf2e1f3ae2597d6aedcdb708006b32ca4698a146a0fdd2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418511405077757973", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04.幻想乐土-The Promised Land-**\n\n没有贫穷、饥饿、疾病、背叛。那是只有花与诗的西岱，那是只属于她们的乐土。\n\nA place free of poverty, hunger, sickness, and betrayal. A Cité of only flowers and poems, a haven that belongs to them alone.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:17:53.638000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418511404327112755", "filename": "4.-The_Promised_Land-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1441166, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511404327112755/4.-The_Promised_Land-.mp3?ex=69ccd4b1&is=69cb8331&hm=6be1189034119801ff1600d0ac5ab6cb1da179ae747475ef933116d420b405b1&"}, {"id": "1418511404813783100", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1703862, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511404813783100/4.jpg?ex=69ccd4b1&is=69cb8331&hm=e8bf02cad129c9f7b67b947c899d7aacce1751876a9569b2dd9f5a5a53e983a1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418511519263752242", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05.如彩云相逐-Like Chasing Clouds-**\n\n花园的草地上，她们仰望云朵随着风变幻。\n柯蕾特，你看，那两朵追逐的云彩，是蝴蝶夫人与毛毛虫先生正在跳舞。\n\nOn the garden's lawn, they lie gazing at the clouds, watching them shift with the wind.\nColette, look! Those two clouds chasing each other: that’s Madame Butterfly and Monsieur Caterpillar dancing.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:18:20.862000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418511518730948658", "filename": "5.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1718936, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511518730948658/5.jpg?ex=69ccd4cc&is=69cb834c&hm=7940bac6242cabb3462e3bd8e99715272e6f6375c2928242b01dff66f66561b7&"}, {"id": "1418511519003574333", "filename": "5.-Like_Chasing_Clouds-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1529355, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511519003574333/5.-Like_Chasing_Clouds-.mp3?ex=69ccd4cc&is=69cb834c&hm=fd99a6ba43a223a65756a32485745e7bab0744889208e0e21b580de673f89b16&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418511662347976764", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06.诗中世界-The World Within a Poem-**\n\n西岱的繁花向您发来邀请，邀请您与它们一同走入这场梦境。\nThe blossoms of Cité extend their invitation, beckoning you to join them in this dream.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:18:54.976000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418511661496668210", "filename": "6.-The_World_Within_a_Poem-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1128950, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511661496668210/6.-The_World_Within_a_Poem-.mp3?ex=69ccd4ee&is=69cb836e&hm=abc7308bfe5d4851bb7aca82a791d488f5612b93c51e5ed1b331d4f2d0afef5a&"}, {"id": "1418511662016757862", "filename": "6.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1707551, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511662016757862/6.jpg?ex=69ccd4ee&is=69cb836e&hm=4c77ca21425a4d1a27ef47bd0fa9220fc21d0063cdce1c0ebac2913431f1068c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418511761195274302", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07.对立的修辞-A Rhetoric of Opposition-**\n\n为何一场大火就能烧毁所有的誓言？\n为何在诗歌的世界里也充满了苦难？\n\nWhy can a single fire burn away all promises?\nWhy is the world of poetry also filled with so much sorrow?", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:19:18.543000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418511760859861082", "filename": "7.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1718561, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511760859861082/7.jpg?ex=69ccd506&is=69cb8386&hm=eee75dca5da023b21eb3e8924dcb56337281cf4bfa74f490632b766c1beb48dc&"}, {"id": "1418511761157652613", "filename": "7.-A_Rhetoric_of_Opposition-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 2212301, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511761157652613/7.-A_Rhetoric_of_Opposition-.mp3?ex=69ccd506&is=69cb8386&hm=da90d907f7a242410b44f0571d88ca2cb5072dd002bc95720d54f71ebbeb5fa6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418511883232743454", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**08.花园往事-Garden Memories-**\n\n花园的残屑与往事的灰烬落在这片小小的土地上。它们在悲哀的回忆里漫天飘扬，它们在狂热的野心里烟消云散。\n\nFragments of the garden and the ashes of memory fall upon this tiny place. They drift mournfully in a haze of sorrow and vanish in the fever of ambition.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:19:47.639000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418511882461122662", "filename": "8.-Garden_Memories-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1419850, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511882461122662/8.-Garden_Memories-.mp3?ex=69ccd523&is=69cb83a3&hm=48635a4346c221f5fe9c86bafb3a12ce05e61fe27f4993583abadd97ebee3aee&"}, {"id": "1418511882939011083", "filename": "8.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1705338, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418511882939011083/8.jpg?ex=69ccd523&is=69cb83a3&hm=89293f73e8b2ac4a2bb899f6535f861f16b0f910e50ed9c9e51f6747ad97d7df&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418512001537151016", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**09.西岱盛典-Grand Celebration-**\n\n诗歌，情感，回忆，道德……一切都是累赘。这个道理，诗人们从不明白。\n在这个世界，人们永远只为权力与名望而庆祝。\n\nPoetry, emotion, memory, morality… all are burdens. It's a truth poets never seem to grasp.\nIn this world, people only ever celebrate power and fame.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:20:15.845000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418512000971046943", "filename": "9.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1710006, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418512000971046943/9.jpg?ex=69ccd53f&is=69cb83bf&hm=875765a9948eebb27ae8f3503b5123f4683e005de244c4f88948e032811ba34e&"}, {"id": "1418512001227034644", "filename": "9.-Grand_Celebration-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 719350, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418512001227034644/9.-Grand_Celebration-.mp3?ex=69ccd53f&is=69cb83bf&hm=61172965f73a1083a35bd35f31dbc131973b4682cc50a211b841fe7493daf607&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418512101449924699", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**10.最后的诗篇-The Last Verse-**\n\n每写下一段诗句，便会长出一片花瓣吧，她想。\n她用生命浇灌字句，当最后的诗篇完成，她们便能回到曾经的花园。\n\nShe thinks, With every line of poetry I write, a petal will grow.\nShe nourishes the words with her life; once the final poem is complete, they will be able to return to the garden of the past.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:20:39.666000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🌹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1418512100556410910", "filename": "10.-The_Last_Verse-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1920983, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418512100556410910/10.-The_Last_Verse-.mp3?ex=69ccd557&is=69cb83d7&hm=e0b453bbcdb6bb93058eb062851200fcaff2fec7f7280c68933fb955d1281f67&"}, {"id": "1418512101013585930", "filename": "10.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1713457, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418512101013585930/10.jpg?ex=69ccd557&is=69cb83d7&hm=d420b8d7cc9c746d725ece7edb496932990a731f93b81c289d4cbadd4dbd19cd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1418512205833306176", "channel_id": "1418510528275546203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**11.玫瑰啊，玫瑰-Rose, Oh Rose-**\n\n用一朵玫瑰，来换一首诗吧。\n在人们荒寂的心脏里，玫瑰正殷红地栖居。\n\nOne rose, for a poem.\nIn our desolate hearts, the roses dwell in deep red.", "timestamp": "2025-09-19T08:21:04.553000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1418512205166547054", "filename": "11.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1719288, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418512205166547054/11.jpg?ex=69ccd570&is=69cb83f0&hm=44d4858db16b933e4c8a33273a0523999c5dcb5845c560d2141f7dcd37dc1d85&"}, {"id": "1418512205481115738", "filename": "11.-Rose_Oh_Rose-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 1937283, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1418510528275546203/1418512205481115738/11.-Rose_Oh_Rose-.mp3?ex=69ccd570&is=69cb83f0&hm=7b2ac1beaef093f2c0393917d7b808382fa75c0d67aefe49de7438f3a9e6ce4c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418510528275546203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：奥尔拉EP·献给春天的花束", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
